vmime:
* POP3, IMAP, SMTP, maildir and sendmail
* SSL/TLS security layer and X.509 certificates (using GNU TLS)
* SASL authentication (using GNU SASL)

Evolution:
	* IMAP:
		* server
		* user
		* crypt: no/TLS/SSL
		* Auth: pass/(NTLM/SPA)/GSSAPI/DIGEST-MD5/CRAM-MD5
	* POP3:
		* server
		* user
		* crypt: ...
		* Auth: pass/APOP/регистрация/...
	* SMTP:
		* 